snippet.title: When The Past Was Around - Prologue Trailer
snippet.description:
The prologue of When the Past was Around, an upcoming adventure point-and-click puzzle game about love, moving on, and letting go is available on Steam now!

Play the prologue for free : http://bit.ly/wpwa-prologue

And don't forget to wishlist the full game: http://bit.ly/wpwa-steam
